      "settings": {
        "html": "<h2 style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:28px; font-weight:700; border-bottom:2px solid #c9a040; padding-bottom:10px; margin:0 0 28px;\">Your Path</h2>\n\n<!-- TIER 1: FREE -->\n<div style=\"background:#f7f7f5; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-top:4px solid #888; border-radius:4px; padding:24px 24px; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0;\">Start Here</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#888; margin:0;\">Free</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#444; font-size:15px; line-height:1.55; margin:0 0 16px;\">No membership required. Access FSI's free resources and start connecting with the real estate professional community.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:10px;\">\n    <div style=\"padding:12px 14px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:4px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">MortgagePoint</p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">MP Daily newsletter, digital magazine, and MP Access podcast</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:12px 14px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:4px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">FSI Offers</p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Free cash offer aggregation on any property address, unlimited</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:12px 14px; background:#fff; border:1px solid #e0e0dc; border-radius:4px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#1f365c; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Community</p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#666; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Social communities, select free courses and webinars</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- TIER 2: ALLIANCE -->\n<div style=\"background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border-radius:6px; padding:28px 28px; margin-bottom:20px;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:10px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"color:#fff; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0;\">Five Star Alliance</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#c9a040; margin:0;\">$495 per year</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#cfd5de; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 18px;\">FSI's universal membership and the entry point for every real estate professional in this community. Alliance is not an introductory offer. It is the membership foundation that FORCE builds on, and it delivers real value on its own.</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; margin:0 0 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Events</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Discounted registration to Five Star Conference and all FSI events</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Media</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Full MortgagePoint subscription with discounted media placement</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Education</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Select complimentary courses, 20% off all educational offerings</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">FSI Offers Platform</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Monthly leads, lead intelligence, marketing tools, skip trace</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Community</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Community Corner profile eligibility in MortgagePoint</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Channel Discounts</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">10% off all FSI channel offerings, advertising and sponsorships</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#cfd5de; font-style:italic; font-size:13px; margin:0 0 12px;\">One additional closing per year more than covers the cost of membership.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;\"><a href=\"mailto:membership@thefivestar.com\" style=\"color:#c9a040; font-weight:600; font-size:14px;\">Contact us about Five Star Alliance &rarr;</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- TIER 3: FORCE -->\n<div style=\"position:relative; background:#1f365c; color:#fff; border-radius:6px; padding:28px 28px; margin-bottom:32px; border:2px solid #c9a040;\">\n  <span style=\"position:absolute; top:-10px; left:24px; background:#c9a040; color:#1f365c; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; padding:4px 12px; border-radius:3px;\">Destination Credential</span>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; flex-wrap:wrap; margin:6px 0 4px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"color:#fff; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0;\">FORCE</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:600; color:#c9a040; margin:0;\">$1,495 per year</p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:12px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 14px;\">Certification Required</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#cfd5de; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 16px;\">FORCE is the destination credential for REO and distressed-property specialists. A vetted membership &mdash; current insurance, certifications, and HUD-compliant background checks &mdash; built on 15 years of practitioner credentialing through Five Star Academy. That rigor is why FORCE is the designation institutional professionals recognize when building their practitioner networks. The FORCE Red Book is distributed nationally to asset managers, keeping members visible where REO referrals originate.</p>\n  <p style=\"color:#fff; font-weight:700; font-size:14px; margin:0 0 12px;\">Everything in Five Star Alliance, plus:</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:10px; margin:0 0 14px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">FORCE Red Book</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Directory distributed to servicer-side asset managers nationally</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">FORCE Connect</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Structured time with institutional professionals at FSI events</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Complimentary Registration</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Five Star Conference and FSI events included with membership</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Advisory Council Eligibility</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Voice in credentialing standards and community direction</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Priority MP Coverage</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">Editorial features and thought leadership positioning</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:4px; padding:12px 14px;\">\n      <p style=\"color:#c9a040; font-size:13px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; margin:0 0 6px;\">Highest FSI Offers Allocation</p>\n      <p style=\"color:#bfc5cf; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; margin:0;\">25 enriched leads per month, lowest overage rate</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"color:#cfd5de; font-size:13px; line-height:1.55; margin:0 0 12px;\">FORCE certification is administered through Five Star Academy. The certification course ($395) is offered at Velocity, Five Star Conference, and online.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;\"><a href=\"mailto:membership@thefivestar.com\" style=\"color:#c9a040; font-weight:600; font-size:14px;\">Contact us about FORCE certification &rarr;</a></p>\n</div>"
      },
